high_descs: Turn around, go to the foot stool in front of the chair.
Take the credit card from the foot stool.
Turn right, go to the black stand next to the piano.
Turn the lamp on that is on the right of the stand.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a credit card near a lit lamp.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the coffee table
Grab the credit card on the coffee table
Turn right, walk to the black table by the floor lamp
anns.task_desc: Grab the credit card on the coffee table, turn on the floor lamp

high_descs: Turn to the left then turn to left and stop in front of the ottoman.
Pick up credit card that is on the ottoman.
Turn right then turn left then turn right to the desk.
Put the credit card on the deck.
anns.task_desc: Put the credit card on the desk.
